{"tid":1799904,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！機電工程署摑陳帆一巴","createTime":"2019-12-27T10:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T05:05:42.000Z","uid":74778,"like":655,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"552b14566e31b41bbcd7b8cdafae41e880dd41d5","tid":1799904,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191226/60419522?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F60419522%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=21b89224\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F60419522%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=d4712851\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191226/60419522?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【東鐵出軌】摑陳帆一巴！機電署還黑衣人清白 確認路軌非遭惡意破壞</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【新增動新聞】<br />\n東鐵綫列車在9月中，發生回歸以來最嚴重的列車出軌意外。一列開往紅磡的列車在駛進月台前，其中三卡突然出軌，列車並斷開兩截，釀成8人受傷。事後有內地媒體隨即「砌生豬肉」，將事件與早前反修例抗爭者扔障礙物入露天軌道事件拉上關係，甚至有內地網民未有實質證據，誣衊臆測是「黑衣暴徒」所為。就連運輸及房屋局局長陳帆，回應事件是否涉及示威活動時亦不置可否，竟稱不排除任何可能性，被轟助謠言滋長。<br />\n<br />\n事隔3個多月，陳帆被他出任問責官員前，曾長年任職的機電工程署「摑一巴」。商業電台今早播出機電工程署署長薛永恒專訪，薛表示，港鐵列車出軌事故的調查工作已到尾聲，署方已排除事故是外物或惡意破壞所致，並確認是鐵路設施本身問題，目前正審視列車出軌意外，是否涉及人為疏忽和制度問題。薛永恒表明，如果調查中發現任何人或機構要承擔責任，將會採取相應的紀律及執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵相繼發生「炒車」甚至出軌意外，薛永恒強調，機電工程署在未來5年，會於各條鐵路線，逐條全面檢視港鐵路軌和訊號等系統的管理及安全制度，加強鐵路安全。<br />\n<br />\n機電署發言人表示，因應港鐵東鐵綫紅磡站列車出軌，該署正進行全面調查，並已聘請本地及海外專家協助，初步已排除事故是由外物或惡意破壞所致。調查工作預計於2020年2月底前完成。"},{"pid":"25453a547689fbf8f47fa8dc71330755ed8508a3","tid":1799904,"uid":143151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53d757ee767a58165b9f644f18b9b133500a80f","tid":1799904,"uid":72863,"like":204,"dislike":2,"score":202,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"班藍絲死撚晒去邊？"},{"pid":"2c708c1f612a2e86b012c8678afac5f4b2ff4080","tid":1799904,"uid":41423,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"同自然定律割席"},{"pid":"7448b7779a16c55f61e30254e0255eb5dc253219","tid":1799904,"uid":266755,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:06:58.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"75345289b453b8d57883e5308d22dde3d87f564a","tid":1799904,"uid":808,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"陳帆本身都係機電署既人"},{"pid":"837942724875c2c67fd92cd95178277daf65653b","tid":1799904,"uid":51932,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"quote":{"pid":"c53d757ee767a58165b9f644f18b9b133500a80f","tid":1799904,"uid":72863,"like":204,"dislike":2,"score":202,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"班藍絲死撚晒去邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:10:22.000Z","msg":"睇唔到㗎喇<br />\n<br />\n藍絲就係咁無恥"},{"pid":"e04bfbefd2571ce2f6b969f91f0e625effaf3488","tid":1799904,"uid":8014,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"其實小學雞都知無可能<br />\n<br />\n小市民邊有可能咁易有工具可以搞得到裂路軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d209ee640a25d974542359bd68d226ee7748afb","tid":1799904,"uid":158,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\